Bug Title: Random Date Generator becomes unresponsive 
Preconditions: None

Steps
Launch the Random Date Generator - https://codebeautify.org/generate-random-date.
In the 'How many dates to generate?' field, enter 0's till 100000 is displayed.

Observed Result
After 100000 is displayed, the Random Date Generator bexcomes unresponsive and the page needs to be refreshed.

Expected Result
The Random Date Generator should not become unresponsive - there is no text telling the user what the limit is.

Test Setup
Chrome v146.0.7680.155
MS Edge 146.0.3856.78
Firefox v149.0
PC with Windows 11 Pro
